           perform   qry-rou-pri-740      thru qry-rou-pri-741        .
           perform   qry-rou-pri-730      thru qry-rou-pri-731        .
           perform   qry-rou-pri-720      thru qry-rou-pri-721        .
           perform   qry-rou-pri-710      thru qry-rou-pri-711        .
